Look for some reference to evaluating determinants by expanding by
minors (or cofactors). That is probably the most general method. Here
is one such discussion:

  Expansion by Minors
  http://mathforum.org/library/drmath/view/51992.html

Here is another:

  Solving 3x3 Matrices Manually
  http://mathforum.org/library/drmath/view/55480.html

If you have any further questions, feel free to write back.


